    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find Alert! This stunning vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! Every inch of this car reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the spotless, like-new interior. The engine runs beautifully, all systems perform perfectly, and there's zero deferred maintenance to worry about. If you've been searching for a car that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is your moment. Come see it in person \u2014 you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46000.0,
